title: SET_MODEL_AS_NO_LONGER_NEEDED

0xE532F5D78798DAAB0xAE0F069E// SetModelAsNoLongerNeeded
void SET_MODEL_AS_NO_LONGER_NEEDED(Hash model);Parameters:model: The model to release ownership of.Releases the script ownership assigned by REQUEST_MODEL. This command should be used when done using a specific model hash in script.
